Worth underscoring TWO #COVID19 #vaccine applications approved in #Canada today: @AstraZeneca & separate @SerumInstIndia version of same vaccine.
One reason this is important: #SII version was intended to serve lower income states; Canada is now dipping into that supply. 🇮🇳💉🌐🇨🇦 https://t.co/GFvoLtQ1kF https://t.co/bNk0NSg08p
